The MineZ team has been hard at work this month to bring you tons of awesome Christmas events! Additionally, the MineZ team has made a claficiation regarding world downloading which can be found [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/clarification-world-downloading.381781/']here[/URL].
 
[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=4][B]SMASH Updates[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
The SMASH team has taken a vote on maps that will be [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/map-purge-maps-to-be-removed.381505/']purged[/URL] and maps that will be [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/map-purge-returning-maps.381499/']returning[/URL] in the next update. Additionally, SMASH had a lot of awesome community events this month! Stay tuned for broadcasts to catch the next ones!
 
